data.description: Adorable move-in ready bungalow in the Happy Valley neighborhood. This two bedroom, one bath home is just a few minutes to downtown Fairhaven, interurban trails, Joe’s Garden, with easy I-5 access. The home has an updated roof, windows and a mini split. The home is situated on a large lot and backyard with mature landscaping, an outbuilding, and plenty of off-street parking for cars, RV, Boat, toys etc. This is a must see!
